  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Continental buffet breakfast with additional hot options is served between 7.30-10.30am.</p>
<p>A three course evening meals with choice of menu and waiter service is served each day. The modern menus include classic dishes as well as mountain specialties and the cuisine is refined and generous with contemporary flavours. Savoyard specialties are available upon request with no supplement and you can upgrade for the À La Carte menu locally. Dinner service is usually between 7-9.30pm.</p>
<p>You can choose between a table in the restaurant or have dinner in the unique heated outdoor pods, be sure to reserve your pod reception.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included on 24th and 31st December. Special dietary requirements such as gluten free, vegetarian and vegans can be catered for but please let us know in advance.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
