  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p>There are three south-facing outdoor terraces with wonderful views, one of which includes the outdoor heated swimming pool, cosmic sauna and whirlpool. This area, La Terrace de la Ferme d'Hubert, is open 10am - 7pm and children must be accompanied by an adult.</p>
<p>The Spa des Alpes Wellness Area has a sensory pool with a variety of themes, hammam, sauna, ice fountain, waterfall bucket, sensorial shower, copper bathtubs and six treatment rooms with numerous massage and beauty treatments available to book locally. There is a local fee to use the Spa des Alpes, it is approx. €25 per person for a 45 minute session.</p>
<p>The hotel also offers:</p>
<ul>
<li>Wine, Cheese &amp; Tapas Bar </li>
<li>Cocktail bar with live evening music (6-10pm)</li>
<li>Lounge with open fireplace</li>
<li>Events rooms for conferences and seminars</li>
<li>Games room</li>
<li>Home cinema</li>
<li>Ski shop on site with heated ski lockers (charge of €3 per day if not rented from the shop) </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
